{"tid":2215934,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無業漢疑冒警查印度漢被起訴 保釋申請被拒","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:31:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3305f53f4f50d9265cc339d59df3a11772613e7","tid":2215934,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:21:04.000Z","msg":"無業男疑於深宵冒警，在深水埗街頭「截查」印度籍男子，稱要查看其身份證及銀包，但印漢堅持要求他出示委任證，結果無業男僅出示自己的身份證，印漢拒絕受查並報警處理。無業男被控冒充公職人員罪，今押解至西九龍法院提堂，案件押後，被告申請保釋被拒。案情透露，被告當時涉身藏手銬、氣槍及BB彈，須有待化驗後才答辯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/T6QXZ65PEFBB5LRPQVLET5ET34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FT6QXZ65PEFBB5LRPQVLET5ET34%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=e37b7617\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FT6QXZ65PEFBB5LRPQVLET5ET34%2F&h=03ecd4b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/T6QXZ65PEFBB5LRPQVLET5ET34/</a>"},{"pid":"875b59dd28af6f23c0173ad7feb2ca55ee8daa27","tid":2215934,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97aecb7a4f0343437c476350a5a5ce81c173b36","tid":2215934,"uid":107681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"自己拎身份證出黎做咩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句證你老母咪扮我似"},{"pid":"26aedeec337ba65b24343533062adf6a9746afdc","tid":2215934,"uid":171786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a97aecb7a4f0343437c476350a5a5ce81c173b36","tid":2215934,"uid":107681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"自己拎身份證出黎做咩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句證你老母咪扮我似"},"cite